Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.30,0:00:16.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在被星光照射的顶屋里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:16.90,0:00:23.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,独自一人聆听着天空的声音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:23.55,0:00:29.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用玻璃的绷带遮住眼睛行走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.20,0:00:36.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家都是孤独的马戏团孩子啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:37.85,0:00:44.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,孤身一人的悲伤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:44.10,0:00:45.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,震动的绷带
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:45.87,0:00:50.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,撼动着心灵……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.35,0:01:06.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用温柔的眼神期待与某人的相会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.05,0:01:21.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在我耳边细语“请留在我身边”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:21.27,0:01:26.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Silent Voice

Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:32.30,0:01:36.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,马士文在亚古捷斯的空域死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.64,0:01:39.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是哈曼对这件事毫不在意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.56,0:01:44.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第四十六话 共震
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.07,0:01:50.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这些家伙是谁?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.98,0:01:52.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,古利明的新人类部队
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.95,0:01:54.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新人类部队?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.44,0:01:56.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我方势力薄弱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.07,0:01:57.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请撤退
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.54,0:01:58.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他派那种东西出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.67,0:01:59.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么可能逃走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.98,0:02:10.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来了,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.06,0:02:12.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,准备好了没?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.65,0:02:15.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.51,0:02:19.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了古利明大人\N我们就算牺牲生命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.22,0:02:21.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也要歼灭哈曼的舰队
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.60,0:02:36.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要笑死人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.24,0:02:37.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们算什么阿!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.47,0:02:55.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.10,0:03:04.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姬娜大人,请撤退
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.90,0:03:05.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.87,0:03:07.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是哈曼大人的命令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.59,0:03:12.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姬娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.43,0:03:15.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别冲动\N要衡量情况
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.04,0:03:16.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,捷度...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.81,0:03:18.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.19,0:03:19.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我回去就是了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.89,0:03:23.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,捷度,怎么办?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.07,0:03:25.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这种敌人根本无法应付
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.01,0:03:27.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回去新亚加玛\N在观察战况吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.79,0:04:01.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,布拉度舰长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.92,0:04:03.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.81,0:04:04.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舰长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.91,0:04:07.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幸好你回来了\N莉娜.桑达
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.78,0:04:11.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她是救我的人...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.55,0:04:14.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道,马茜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.21,0:04:17.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好久不见了,布拉度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.90,0:04:19.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,马茜...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.50,0:04:21.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在地球的表现很活跃阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.71,0:04:24.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一个女人能做到什么程度\N那是可想而知的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.45,0:04:29.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来,这是你太太与你儿子的录影带
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.25,0:04:31.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.88,0:04:33.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.20,0:04:35.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你至少该写封信阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.69,0:04:39.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在第三殖民地的战况好像很紧张
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.43,0:04:42.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的,许多年轻人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.97,0:04:45.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也在那个空域战斗阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.70,0:04:47.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像过去的你们一样...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.51,0:04:48.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.23,0:04:57.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我打算去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.81,0:05:00.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第三殖民地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.14,0:05:01.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.76,0:05:04.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我哥哥马沙的下落吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.90,0:05:07.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没时间搜索他阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.55,0:05:11.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这场战争完全感觉不到\N马沙的个人意识
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.77,0:05:14.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,连哈曼的也没有感觉到吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.47,0:05:15.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.69,0:05:18.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也许他在某个地方\N看着我们所做的事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.82,0:05:20.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且在沉思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.36,0:05:23.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想说他在等候时机吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.14,0:05:25.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这确实是我哥哥的作风阿...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.17,0:05:28.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不觉得危险吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.48,0:05:31.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有想念的新人类是很可悲的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.83,0:05:37.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在做准备\N等着感到厌烦而展开行动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.54,0:05:39.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不想看哥哥变成那种人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.85,0:05:41.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他干脆死了算了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.46,0:05:42.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.81,0:05:44.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,野心与纷争
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.73,0:05:51.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得哥哥好像\N会被宇宙的大意至左右着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.11,0:05:53.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是这样吗...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.19,0:05:58.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是谁!是谁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.41,0:06:02.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,擅自跑到我的脑中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.22,0:06:03.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.62,0:06:09.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,波蕾二世在干什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.30,0:06:13.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全面通知新人类部队
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.14,0:06:14.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.83,0:06:16.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把孟沙切离开去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.28,0:06:18.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是,孟沙分离
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.78,0:06:27.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,孟沙分离完毕了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.14,0:06:29.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,修正方向
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.60,0:06:31.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让孟沙去撞击哈曼军舰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.55,0:06:32.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.28,0:06:37.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈曼\N想统治世界的野心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.89,0:06:39.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是造成你毁灭的原因阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.58,0:06:45.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚古捷斯的孟沙开始移动了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.81,0:06:48.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们想用那巨物撞上哈曼舰队
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.73,0:06:50.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此,先撞散敌人编队
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.85,0:06:53.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在一口气击灭新人类部队
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.09,0:06:55.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到时候战力比例就不是问题了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.92,0:06:56.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,捷度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.47,0:06:59.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新人类部队交给我解决吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.21,0:07:01.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等阿,捷度,补给...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.10,0:07:02.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没那个时间了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.64,0:07:04.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在不打败古利明的话...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.23,0:07:07.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奥干的舰队在干什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.43,0:07:09.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要拖到什么时候才来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.77,0:07:12.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这些杂乱的东西是什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.89,0:07:13.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,行动多不方便阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.97,0:07:15.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是飞盘
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.55,0:07:18.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,丢出去使用\N可以混乱敌人耳目
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.14,0:07:21.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ZZ高达,出动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.80,0:07:33.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,孟沙开始炮击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.95,0:07:35.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舰队分散开去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.87,0:07:37.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叫MS队上前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.53,0:07:38.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.71,0:07:41.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,孟沙是新吉翁的象征
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.35,0:07:43.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他竟然拿来当盾牌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.98,0:07:46.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可恶的古利明,真该死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.33,0:07:53.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了?波蕾二世
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.90,0:07:56.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我来守后方\N你上前吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.36,0:07:58.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了,达卡恩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.03,0:08:01.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来了来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.56,0:08:04.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尼伊,蓝斯,那家伙给我对付吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.05,0:08:11.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我说过不会让你过去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.43,0:08:14.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你偷走哈曼大人的\N亚古捷斯还可以说什么话?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.74,0:08:16.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,孟沙还你们了不是吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.90,0:08:18.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,开什么玩笑!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.34,0:08:26.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哼,你能逃到什么时候?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.63,0:08:32.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姬娜,住手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.21,0:08:35.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么?有别的气势
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.88,0:08:40.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那光波没什么...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.23,0:08:43.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你完了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.41,0:08:49.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尼伊!姬娜大人拜托你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.67,0:08:52.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要碍事,滚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.08,0:08:56.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蓝斯!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.19,0:08:58.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姬娜大人,请退后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.87,0:09:00.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,休想逃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.62,0:09:04.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住手!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.63,0:09:06.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦?是那家伙...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.95,0:09:17.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打中了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.49,0:09:22.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这种程度的飞弹不算什么阿\N波蕾二世
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.19,0:09:27.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可以去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.32,0:09:29.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别妨碍捷度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.08,0:09:31.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快离开这架MS吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.45,0:09:36.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刚才想闯入我体内的是你吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.35,0:09:38.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,捷度不是敌人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.43,0:09:42.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟捷度在一起很舒服的\N为什么你不了解阿?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.00,0:09:43.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别过来!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.53,0:09:45.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要使我混乱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.28,0:09:50.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么?打中了却没效
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.75,0:09:53.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是有奇怪的盾牌吗?波蕾二世
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.96,0:09:55.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,消失吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.90,0:09:57.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.03,0:10:09.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,臭小子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.51,0:10:14.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.92,0:10:17.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那只是小孩在驾驶阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:23.26,0:10:25.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,波蕾二世,回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.04,0:10:27.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别听古利明的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.49,0:10:29.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,代理舰长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.71,0:10:32.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚古捷斯的防卫线断了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.32,0:10:34.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈曼的MS部队冲进去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.96,0:10:36.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,高达队伍呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.39,0:10:38.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,捷度他们怎么了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.20,0:10:40.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像进入防卫线里面\N
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.33,0:10:42.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他们只有三架MS...就跑去亚古捷斯?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.79,0:11:03.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反击太慢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.85,0:11:12.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要撞上了\N不,擦过而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.21,0:11:21.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,孟沙航道改变了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.33,0:11:22.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.67,0:11:25.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我方战力减少15%
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.33,0:11:28.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚古捷斯加快速度\N什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.29,0:11:30.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让亚古捷斯和柯亚3接触
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.95,0:11:32.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.32,0:11:35.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈曼...这次不会向孟沙那样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.48,0:11:37.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给你轻易必过去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.72,0:11:48.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,波蕾二世,你在哪里?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.12,0:11:55.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,露卡,捷度进去里面了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.73,0:11:57.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他想死吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.07,0:11:59.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去吧\N真是的...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.70,0:12:14.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,确认方位\N这次换亚古捷斯过来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.66,0:12:17.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们不能丧失亚古捷失的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.18,0:12:20.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,派间谍\N潜入亚古捷思改变方向
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.26,0:12:21.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.86,0:12:28.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是...我知道了,捷度\N你进入亚古捷斯了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.33,0:12:32.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,古利明就在里面吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.30,0:12:42.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敌人MS进入M区
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.96,0:12:44.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可能是高达
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.68,0:12:47.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我方的MS部队在干什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.77,0:12:49.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,波蕾二世的情况很奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.95,0:12:51.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.03,0:12:53.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她直接飞回来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:53.25,0:12:54.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.73,0:12:57.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.51,0:13:06.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,波蕾二世,怎么了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.27,0:13:10.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的精神催眠\N不是最完美了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.16,0:13:11.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,照理说应该是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.54,0:13:12.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是为什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.68,0:13:15.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刚才她的波动太混乱了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.20,0:13:18.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,古利明...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.50,0:13:21.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,波蕾二世,为什么回来?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.36,0:13:24.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,波蕾...波蕾在妨碍我啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.55,0:13:25.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,波蕾?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.69,0:13:29.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你振作一点\N波蕾在很久以前就死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.74,0:13:32.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她是被高达骗了阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.11,0:13:35.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打倒他,这样...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.36,0:13:37.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的头痛会好吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.80,0:13:39.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,会的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.23,0:13:43.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以你的力量必须送给古利明我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.74,0:13:46.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,古利明大人,你要干什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.22,0:13:51.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已你和我的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.16,0:13:54.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把高达打进宇宙的黑暗之中吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.43,0:13:59.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,捷度,你去哪里?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.14,0:14:05.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Z高达?是露卡吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.59,0:14:07.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.77,0:14:14.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了,打倒想束缚你的敌人吧,波蕾二世
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.35,0:14:16.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,束缚我的,敌人...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.05,0:14:21.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.77,0:14:37.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主荧幕...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.12,0:14:38.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.38,0:14:41.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有人可以妨碍我们前进的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.51,0:14:43.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说的对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.06,0:14:48.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,露卡!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.58,0:15:00.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,捷度,你在干什么阿?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.06,0:15:03.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉!你在哪里?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.85,0:15:07.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉,快逃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.61,0:15:09.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了,可是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.94,0:15:14.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,波蕾二世
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:14.13,0:15:17.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,杀死那个高达,就会舒服些的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.31,0:15:19.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,消灭它? \N对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.39,0:15:20.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说的对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.93,0:15:25.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住手,波蕾二世!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.25,0:15:28.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,捷度过来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.51,0:15:29.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.71,0:15:39.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为古利明做事对你没有益处的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.00,0:15:41.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你害我痛苦的要命\N还说什么风凉话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.45,0:15:42.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.57,0:15:44.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是你必须打倒的敌人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.90,0:15:46.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放手!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.04,0:15:51.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想当古利明的木偶吗?波蕾二世!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.49,0:15:55.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,波蕾二世,回来,他是敌人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.86,0:15:58.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,波蕾二世!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.10,0:16:02.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,波蕾二世,古利明是拿你当道具的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.15,0:16:05.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有非战不可的正义阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.16,0:16:08.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而你没有正义,你为何而战呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.32,0:16:10.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.56,0:16:12.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,捷度..
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.01,0:16:19.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你打仗,是因为你是士兵
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.32,0:16:22.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你驾驶高达,是情势所逼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.86,0:16:25.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是我不同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.28,0:16:27.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我自己选择苛刻的生存方式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.67,0:16:29.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不会后悔的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.42,0:16:32.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你没有由心理涌起的冲动吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.47,0:16:35.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像你这种人渣\N从我面前消失吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.44,0:16:36.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.87,0:16:41.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道这里的人已经因为欲望\N而扭曲理念犯错了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.73,0:16:44.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我...所以我...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.09,0:16:51.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你感受的忿怒和不平就是理由啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.19,0:16:56.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘉美尤不是受人命令的\N他是自愿战斗的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.10,0:16:59.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他相信它能拯救世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.14,0:17:03.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥,相信自己的心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.57,0:17:06.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是波蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.11,0:17:10.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.17,0:17:13.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不会错的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.87,0:17:19.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是背负大家的意识而战的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.03,0:17:21.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家的意识?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.77,0:17:24.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说的好像很有道理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.13,0:17:26.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我问你,你的原点来自何处?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.64,0:17:28.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是地球吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.09,0:17:32.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,培育一切生命的地球吧,是我们的故乡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.50,0:17:34.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沙比家的血统
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.00,0:17:36.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只占其中数千亿分之一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:36.85,0:17:38.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果非要为了那血统而战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.87,0:17:40.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你留在亚古捷斯就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.09,0:17:43.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,地球受到污染
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.84,0:17:47.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们殖民地又旧又腐败
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.60,0:17:51.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在人类全体\N必须重头再来才可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.70,0:17:54.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像你这种为小事\N而耿耿于怀的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.85,0:17:58.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不打倒你,地球就没有明天了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.30,0:18:02.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被血统束缚的人\N是人类的绊脚石
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.52,0:18:03.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,捷度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.64,0:18:08.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不能容许人类的这个可能性\N为了你的自我满足而被握脆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.87,0:18:09.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是哥哥吗...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.46,0:18:13.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,头好痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.29,0:18:16.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要有他的存在\N你的头痛是不会停止的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.40,0:18:17.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.21,0:18:20.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,波蕾二世,捷度说的对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.70,0:18:22.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,波蕾二世
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.58,0:18:24.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,捷度吗...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.67,0:18:27.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,过来吧\N波蕾二世
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.40,0:18:28.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,波蕾...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.70,0:18:30.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.32,0:18:32.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是我的一部份
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.31,0:18:34.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别被搞乱阿,过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.77,0:18:36.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,波蕾二世
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.19,0:18:40.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,波蕾二世,战斗吧\N住手阿!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.26,0:18:42.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要被敌人迷惑到何时?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.31,0:18:44.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住手阿!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.73,0:18:47.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我讨厌大家\N全部给我消失吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.59,0:18:51.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这光芒...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.59,0:18:55.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,捷度,快救波蕾二世
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.21,0:18:58.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,波蕾二世想来我们这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.17,0:19:00.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了,波蕾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.48,0:19:03.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对,这样才对的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.48,0:19:04.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,杀死捷度吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.09,0:19:19.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,古利明!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.56,0:19:24.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ZZ高达是打不死的吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.07,0:19:26.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,捷度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.23,0:19:27.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.74,0:19:29.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,消失了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.42,0:19:38.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,古利明\N不许你再利用波蕾二世
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.14,0:19:39.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,少啰唆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.77,0:19:41.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,捷度,带我走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:41.28,0:19:43.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回来\N放开我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.38,0:19:52.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说过你喜欢我\N我不会忘记的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.15,0:20:04.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是你吗?露卡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.91,0:20:07.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我竟然死在你手上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.56,0:20:11.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.32,0:20:24.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,古利明的波动消失了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.44,0:20:27.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,潜入亚古捷斯的间谍\N传回通讯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.91,0:20:30.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚古捷斯的推进装置被破坏了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.55,0:20:32.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没办法改变方位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.99,0:20:34.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全军撤退!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.83,0:20:36.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,MS也后退吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.95,0:20:37.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.45,0:20:41.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你一定要活着回来阿\N捷度.桑达
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.57,0:20:43.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到时候再跟你了结
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.41,0:20:46.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚古捷斯和柯亚3会相撞的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.74,0:20:48.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,捷度他们怎么了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.46,0:20:52.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没办法联络吗?\N不行,无法通讯阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.18,0:20:53.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要去哪里?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.38,0:20:54.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去接人阿!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.76,0:20:57.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样下去会被冲击波波及的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.29,0:20:59.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不能看着他们死掉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.54,0:21:03.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不知道后果多严重\N才会说这种话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.01,0:21:04.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,代理舰长!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.42,0:21:07.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相信捷度他们吧,会逃出来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.26,0:21:10.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对,露卡和艾莉的命很大的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:11.13,0:21:14.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了,新亚加玛,后退
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.77,0:21:36.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爆炸使得亚古捷斯远离了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.31,0:21:37.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,捷度他们呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.07,0:21:50.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚古捷斯的爆炸扩大了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.47,0:21:53.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行,看情况是逃不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.31,0:22:01.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是ZZ高达!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:01.76,0:22:03.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了,捷度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:03.26,0:22:04.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等阿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:04.57,0:22:06.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,MK2和Z高达在哪里?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:06.58,0:22:08.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,捷度,听见了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:08.24,0:22:10.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听见了,伊莱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:10.88,0:22:12.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾莉她们呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:12.22,0:22:14.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她们没事,在我这里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:14.71,0:22:17.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比查,对不起,让你担心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:17.45,0:22:19.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们马上就回来了\N知道了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:20.92,0:22:23.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吓我一跳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:23.10,0:22:24.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:24.78,0:22:28.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,波蕾二世,加油阿\N你不可以死

Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:43.30,0:22:49.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,成百 成万 上亿的繁星啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:49.49,0:22:55.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为何只是闪耀而已 展示你言语的能力吧 
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:55.55,0:23:06.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在我也能不回头地 让心灵出发
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:07.70,0:23:12.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,若能把多如繁星的生命储存的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:13.65,0:23:18.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把整个银河也化作光芒吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:19.35,0:23:28.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,化作紧握在掌心的 生命的重量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:28.32,0:23:33.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我仍未能看见宇宙的路标
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:34.22,0:23:40.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,手掌触摸着一千万年的光芒

Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:45.81,0:23:48.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了和我做个了断 哈曼出击了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:49.28,0:23:51.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,高洁！帅气！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:51.66,0:23:54.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,输了就会死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:54.02,0:23:56.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这可不是在开玩笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:56.07,0:23:58.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是…好强的力量！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:58.23,0:24:01.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“谁来…！”不小心就这样想了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:01.96,0:24:05.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下集 高达ZZ 战士再临
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:06.43,0:24:08.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难道我被哈曼喜欢上了？
